&lt;p&gt;The correct spelling is &amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;leisure&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leisure &lt;/strong&gt;means&amp;nbsp;the time when you do not have to work; free time (समय जिसमें काम नहीं करना होता; ख़ाली समय, फ़ुरसत)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Example-&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;She has a limited amount of leisure time.&lt;br /&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&lt;strong&gt; option 2.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
